metadata.title: Monarch Specialties Dark Taupe Hall Console Accent Table, 48"
features: Ample surface area for displaying pictures, decorative pieces or books
description: Make a bold statement in your living room or hallway with this 48" long dark taupe accent table. Featuring a thick panel design, assymetrical lines and an edgy modern appeal this table will surely make an eye catching addition to your living space. Perfect for displaying pictures, decorative pieces or books this accent table is the perfect combination of fashion and function.
